{"analytics_identifier":"OT328","base_path":"/government/organisations/official-solicitor-and-public-trustee","content_id":"0fac336b-7685-4b1b-bdf1-37e4e964bf67","description":"We help people who are vulnerable because of their lack of mental capacity or young age to take advantage of the services offered by the justice system. This helps them to avoid being socially excluded. OSPT works with the Ministry of Justice .","details":{"acronym":"OSPT","alternative_format_contact_email":"","body":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>We help people who are vulnerable because of their lack of mental capacity or young age to take advantage of the services offered by the justice system. This helps them to avoid being socially excluded.</p>\n\n<p><abbr title=\"Official Solicitor and Public Trustee\">OSPT</abbr> works with the <a class=\"brand__color\" href=\"/government/organisations/ministry-of-justice\">Ministry of Justice</a>.</p>\n</div>","brand":"ministry-of-justice","foi_exempt":false,"logo":{"crest":"single-identity","formatted_title":"Official Solicitor <br/>and Public Trustee"},"ordered_corporate_information_pages":[{"href":"/government/organisations/official-solicitor-and-public-trustee/about/complaints-procedure","title":"Complaints procedure"}],"ordered_featured_documents":[],"ordered_featured_links":[{"href":"https://www.gov.uk/child-maintenance-if-one-parent-lives-abroad","title":"Arrange child maintenance if one parent lives abroad"},{"href":"https://www.gov.uk/return-or-contact-abducted-child","title":"Find help to get your child back from abroad or arrange contact"},{"href":"https://www.gov.uk/tenancy-agreements-a-guide-for-landlords/if-your-tenant-dies-without-an-executor-or-a-will","title":"File a notice to quit when your tenant dies"},{"href":"https://www.gov.uk/check-register-notice-to-quit","title":"Check the end of tenancy has been registered "},{"href":"https://www.gov.uk/public-trustee-executor-will","title":"Appoint the Public Trustee as executor of your estate"},{"href":"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/official-solicitor-and-public-trustee/about#contact-information","title":"Contact OSPT"}],"ordered_promotional_features":[],"organisation_featuring_priority":"service","organisation_govuk_status":{"status":"live","updated_at":null,"url":null},"organisation_political":false,"organisation_type":"other","secondary_corporate_information_pages":"Our <a class=\"govuk-link brand__color\" href=\"/government/organisations/official-solicitor-and-public-trustee/about/personal-information-charter\">Personal information charter</a> explains how we treat your personal information.","social_media_links":[]},"document_type":"organisation","first_published_at":"2012-02-29T11:00:29+00:00","links":{"available_translations":[{"analytics_identifier":"OT328","api_path":"/api/content/government/organisations/official-solicitor-and-public-trustee","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/organisations/official-solicitor-and-public-trustee","base_path":"/government/organisations/official-solicitor-and-public-trustee","content_id":"0fac336b-7685-4b1b-bdf1-37e4e964bf67","document_type":"organisation","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2023-03-28T11:18:27Z","schema_name":"organisation","title":"Official Solicitor and Public Trustee","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/official-solicitor-and-public-trustee","withdrawn":false}],"ordered_board_members":[{"api_path":"/api/content/government/people/sarah-castle","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/people/sarah-castle","base_path":"/government/people/sarah-castle","content_id":"48772c8c-1915-45a2-89d3-9c7239f706e9","details":{"image":{"alt_text":"Sarah Castle","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/6422e7a93d885d000fdadcc0/s465_sarah-castle.png"},"privy_counsellor":false},"document_type":"person","links":{"role_appointments":[{"content_id":"56dd61ba-dcea-42fa-b94b-3cc1c22093d2","details":{"current":true,"ended_on":null,"person_appointment_order":2,"started_on":"2019-07-03T00:00:00+01:00"},"document_type":"role_appointment","links":{"role":[{"content_id":"8477b00e-c0f1-11e4-8223-005056011aef","details":{"body":"<p>The Official Solicitor duties mainly relate to protecting the vulnerable in the justice system, in particular litigants who are children or young persons and those unable to conduct their own litigation due to lack of mental capacity.</p>\n\n<p>The role is, however, wide and varied. See <a href=\"http://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/official-solicitor-and-public-trustee/about#responsibilities\">the full list of duties on our ‘About us’ page</a>.</p>\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2014-11-14T15:59:01Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Official Solicitor","withdrawn":false}]},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2025-08-21T08:22:53Z","schema_name":"role_appointment","title":"Sarah Castle - Official Solicitor","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"d659b2be-0ee4-4fe7-b50b-1bc3b609f014","details":{"current":true,"ended_on":null,"person_appointment_order":5745,"started_on":"2019-07-04T00:00:00+01:00"},"document_type":"role_appointment","links":{"role":[{"content_id":"8477b24b-c0f1-11e4-8223-005056011aef","details":{"body":"<p>The Public Trustee administers trusts and estates where they have accepted appointment to do so and acts as:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>executor and administrator of the estates of the deceased</li>\n  <li>trustee of trusts in the interests of vulnerable individuals or disabled people</li>\n  <li>where there are differences between executors, trustees or beneficiaries</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>The Public Trustee also deals with the recording of applications for notice to quit under the Law of Property (Miscellaneous Provisions) Act 1994.</p>\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2024-05-29T10:35:08Z","schema_name":"role","tit