{"status":"live","updated_at":null,"url":null}},"document_type":"organisation","links":{},"locale":"en","schema_name":"organisation","title":"Ministry of Justice","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/ministry-of-justice","withdrawn":false}],"ordered_roles":[{"content_id":"8477b00e-c0f1-11e4-8223-005056011aef","details":{"body":"<p>The Official Solicitor duties mainly relate to protecting the vulnerable in the justice system, in particular litigants who are children or young persons and those unable to conduct their own litigation due to lack of mental capacity.</p>\n\n<p>The role is, however, wide and varied. See <a href=\"http://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/official-solicitor-and-public-trustee/about#responsibilities\">the full list of duties on our ‘About us’ page</a>.</p>\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2014-11-14T15:59:01Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Official Solicitor","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"8477b24b-c0f1-11e4-8223-005056011aef","details":{"body":"<p>The Public Trustee administers trusts and estates where they have accepted appointment to do so and acts as:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>executor and administrator of the estates of the deceased</li>\n  <li>trustee of trusts in the interests of vulnerable individuals or disabled people</li>\n  <li>where there are differences between executors, trustees or beneficiaries</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>The Public Trustee also deals with the recording of applications for notice to quit under the Law of Property (Miscellaneous Provisions) Act 1994.</p>\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2024-05-29T10:35:08Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Public Trustee","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"8477b360-c0f1-11e4-8223-005056011aef","details":{"body":"<p>A Deputy Official Solicitor carries out the duties of the Official Solicitor in their absence.</p>\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2024-07-22T13:24:40Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Deputy Official Solicitor","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"8477b468-c0f1-11e4-8223-005056011aef","details":{"body":"<p>A Deputy Official Solicitor carries out the duties of the Official Solicitor in their absence.</p>\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2024-07-22T13:30:54Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Deputy Official Solicitor","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"8477b56b-c0f1-11e4-8223-005056011aef","details":{"body":"<p>A Deputy Official Solicitor carries out the duties of the Official Solicitor in their absence.</p>\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2024-07-22T13:25:00Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Deputy Official Solicitor","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"8477b67d-c0f1-11e4-8223-005056011aef","details":{"body":"<p>The Head of Operations is responsible for all elements of service delivery, including budget and staffing, and reports to the Official Solicitor and to the Public Trustee.</p>\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2014-12-08T20:30:19Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Head of Operations","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"0b13954c-fafe-4c2a-b4ac-bad5d89ebc1d","details":{"body":"<p>A Deputy Public Trustee carries out the duties of the Public Trustee in their absence.</p>\n\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2024-07-22T13:35:23Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Deputy Public Trustee","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"171f8037-ccf9-476e-85dd-a081e944c7f9","details":{"body":"<p>The Second Permanent Secretary works closely with the Permanent Secretary on all aspects of Ministry of Justice leadership. Jo holds responsibility for Her Majesty’s Prison and Probation Service and oversight for Legal Aid Agency, Official Solicitor and Public Trustee, Office of the Public Guardian and Criminal Injuries Compensation Authority.</p>\n\n<p>The CEO of HM Prison and Probation Service has the strategic management and accountability of the agency and is a member of Ministry of Justice Departmental Board executive management committee.</p>\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2022-05-24T12:50:55Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Second Permanent Secretary, Ministry of Justice and Chief Executive Officer, HM Prison & Probation Service","withdrawn":false}],"organisations":[{"analytics_identifier":"OT328","api_path":"/api/content/government/organisations/official-solicitor-and-public-trustee","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/organisations/official-solicitor-and-public-trustee","base_path":"/government/organisations/official-solicitor-and-public-trustee","content_id":"0fac336b-7685-4b1b-bdf1-37e4e964bf67","details":{"acronym":"OSPT","brand":"ministry-of-justice","default_news_image":null,"logo":{"crest":"single-identity","formatted_title":"Official Solicitor <br/>and Public Trustee"},"organisation_govuk_status":{"status":"live","updated_at":null,"url":null}},"document_type":"organisation","links":{},"locale":"en","schema_name":"organisation","title":"Official Solicitor and Public Trustee","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/official-solicitor-and-public-trustee","withdrawn":false}],"primary_publishing_organisation":[{"analytics_identifier":"OT328","api_path":"/api/content/government/organisations/official-solicitor-and-public-trustee","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/organisations/official-solicitor-and-public-trustee","base_path":"/government/organisations/official-solicitor-and-public-trustee","content_id":"0fac336b-7685-4b1b-bdf1-37e4e964bf67","details":{"acr